title.rendered: BOSS AIR SUSPENSION GAUGE LINE KIT

content.rendered:
BOSS AIR SUSPENSION GAUGE LINE KIT

Boss Air Suspension Gauge Line Kit available for order now through Automax 4×4! Order online, come in & see us or give us a call on (02) 6699 2744 for a quote!

Gauge Line install kit. Easily run airline into the cab with this smaller diameter airline and connect a Boss dual needle valve gauge.

Includes;

  • 200psi
  • Dual Needle Gauge
  • 10mtrs 4mm DOT Air line
  • 2x 4mm push to connect fittings
  • 2x 4mm x 1/8 male push connect fittings
  • Mounting Bracket

Extra Options Available;

  • 1/4″ Airline Fittings Kit
    • 1/4″ Airline Valve Fitting Kit Sealant-Less
  • Remote Nitto Add-on
    • Add a remote Nitto Coupling so you can “plug-in” to pump up tyres or use air tools
To view the range of Boss Air products available, CLICK HERE!
Follow us on Instagram and Facebook to keep up to date with what’s going on in our workshop!
